Summary: Taking random pictures of the sky and upon viewing this orb shows in one picture
divs: Sighting DetailsMy wife was in a store shopping and I waited outside sitting on a bench. I had my camera with me as I usually do and decided to take some random pictures of the sky hoping for something to show up. I was holding the camera on my knee pointing directly overhead and above me and took several photos straight up. I did not know this object was above me and did not see it. Later while viewing these photos I found this round looking what I call a orb or sphere in one picture. My camera of choice is a Nikon S630 and all setting were set to automatic.
